<p>王维诗-山居秋暝</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201123/90b30581ab7d411dad9f78d27f82d52a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>毛主席词：咏梅</p>